data.description: Seller's loan is assumable, so qualified buyers can get an incredible 2.75% interest rate! Updated and incredibly maintained home in the highly sought after Westbrook Lakes subdivision. Brand new roof and gutters installed September 2023. Galvanized steel gazebo on the back deck and beautiful exterior lighting all the way around create an amazing outdoor experience. Deck is made of incredible TREX material and, along with the gazebo, comes with transferable 25 year warranty. Updated kitchen and master bathroom with stunning shower with two showerheads, and gorgeous living areas throughout. Updates and full remodels in the last few months include new closets, cabinet lighting in the kitchen, cabinets in the laundry room, and cedar fence with railing along the top and mudboard on the bottom. House is fully programmed through Nest so you never have to get up! Zoned to excellent schools and plenty of shopping and entertainment in the area! Don't miss your chance to tour this forever home!
